        <a href="/police-fire/10-license-violators-westchester-fined-state-liquor-authority" data-event-category="NodeClick" data-event-value="961642" data-event-label="MostPopular-Headline">10 License Violators In Westchester Fined By State Liquor Authority </a>      </li>
